From: Dinh Nguyen <dinguyen@altera.com>
Date: Mon, 12 Nov 2012 21:43:03 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 167/254] arm: socfpga: Create a device tree source for ICE

Upstream: git://git.rocketboards.org/linux-socfpga.git

Create a separate device tree source for support on the emulator.

Signed-off-by: Dinh Nguyen <dinguyen@altera.com>
(cherry picked from commit eb03bce5e6ec259df115f2a823ae489b8c507a61)
Signed-off-by: Zumeng Chen <zumeng.chen@windriver.com>
---
